column5: Check out out brand new website .... hope some new fishing friends might make it up for some great Pike and Walleye fishing this summer !  www.xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx.com  Looking forward to hearing from you all !  Gary & Kim
you do understand what spam is don't you  most people will go out of their way to not do business with a spammer

spam is one thing, poor spelling/grammar is another, but this really pushes me away from a business:  *unfortunately, due to the cost of processing, we do not accept Credit Cards at this time.  it's a cost of business and your competitors accept CC's...

Sorry dude, we just don't have the time to look after these things so for the time being, consider yourself in Limbo. (Latin limbus, edge or boundary, referring to the "edge" of Hell). Get your act together, then you might be able to come back. Have a super evening.
